{
  "stem": "27748.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "As a lowly enlisted man, it gave me joy, which is not a very decent thing to do.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I do remember it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Anyway, so-- I mean, actually I'm picking up on that in my recent work, namely that as you go higher and higher in a career, your public image is one of increasing strength, and confidence, and security.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But at the same time, it's possible that your insecurity also grows.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Your vulnerability also grows.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the guy who is at the first rank of general in the army may be terrified of getting a small bad grade that keeps him from being elevated-- making it to the next hoop.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That is, there may be a very great vulnerability at the very highest level.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so we have, in a sense, a double track, many of us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not everybody necessarily, but a double track of a public confidence increasing confidence, but also increasing fears of vulnerability.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That can also grow, and can be tapped into occasionally.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So, anyway, I'm writing about that currently in something.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the army experience was eventually-- the main thing I got from the army was the GI bill.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But also, I had taken books along with me from graduate school.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I had-- I was sort of in the middle of a master's degree program.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I took heavy books with me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I took time to read.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So unlike most of my fellow graduate students, I could devote a lot of time to heavy books, because I had a lot of time.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So in a sense, I got that out of the army too-- the luxury of spending a lot of time with serious books.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was sort of a bland affair.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
